    "rowsha": "jLgcOaJz6nBYthlTlg0VvhhhCz14M/yTjHe6IHeIrXc=",
    "originContent": "4. **重要：** 在 LSPosed 中配置作用域：",
    "translatedContent": "4. **Important :** Configurez le scope dans LSPosed :  "
